A small messanger in local network (Just for fun)

--help  - show this page

-s "path_to_cfg.srv" - start as server (using for retranslate messages) with "path_to_cfg.srv" configuration.

-c server_ip - start as client on "server_ip" server.

--server-cfg "path_to_save"  - configurate server with save it in "path_to_save"

-r server_ip  - register on server_ip server 
